column5: So inspirational 😂 just started this show and I’m hooked.

For the longest I suffered in silence and wouldn’t get help for myself because I was afraid of opening up and put it off for so long...I almost wasn’t here today to see how much better it gets. The last few months have been some of the hardest I’ve had but these last few weeks have been some of the best. Opening up helped me so much..even when my voice shakes and I’m crying so hard I can barely talk ..I have listening ears who don’t judge me for it.


I almost wasn’t here to see how much better things get. Next month makes 2 years free from self harm...I’m glad I stayed.
That’s so amazing and exciting!! So happy for you :)
